<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px;">各位考生：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px;">我校江西省2023年高等职业教育单独招生考试准考证将进行统一发放。领取准考证的时间和地点如下，考生也可以提前查看本人考场信息（附件2）：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px;">时间：2023年3月17日(周五)</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;9:00-16:00</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px;">地点：IBM一楼大厅</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px;">届时请携带本人身份证原件进行领取，如有困难，也可考试当天领取。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px;">如需代领，则需出具考生的委托书（模板见下）及受托人的身份证原件（考生的身份证原件仍需要）；如考生无法在上述时间领取准考证，可联系办公室约定其他时间领取。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px;">联系电话：0791-83792888</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px; text-align: right;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 江西软件职业技术大学招生办</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color: rgb(86, 64, 89); font-family: 楷体;">附件1：江西软件职业技术大学单招准考证代领委托书</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color: rgb(86, 64, 89); font-family: 楷体;">附件2：江西软件职业技术大学2023年单招考试考场信息</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;"><br></p><p><img src="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1722397012366.jpg" alt="1722397012366.jpg" data-href="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1722397012366.jpg" style="width: 100%;"/></p>